asset.title: Jhene Aiko | Soul of Summer Collection
asset.description:
For the first Neff womenswear collabortation, Aiko helped design graphic tees, tanks, dresses, and patterned soft shorts perfect for everyday wear. "The 'Soul of Summer' collection was inspired by my love for summer nights," Aiko told Nylon Magazine. "I used to work at PacSun as a teenager, and I thought it would be awesome to team up with both PacSun and Neff for this collection." 

The collection will be available at PacSun stores and online later this month. Get a sneak peek of the collection in her behind-the-scenes video.
